	<item>
		<title>Why Your Brand Needs a Digital-First Strategy</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>In 2026, a digital-first approach is no longer optional — it's essential. Consumers expect seamless experiences across every touchpoint, and brands that deliver outperform competitors by 3x.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>We break down the key components of a winning digital-first strategy, from unified brand messaging to omnichannel execution.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
