	<item>
		<title>Case Study: How We Tripled Conversions for FinTech Startup</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>A Series A FinTech startup came to us with a great product but poor conversion rates. Their platform was feature-rich but confusing to navigate.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#c9a96e"}}} -->
		<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="color:#c9a96e">The Approach</h3>
		<!-- /wp:heading -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>We redesigned the user journey, simplified the onboarding flow, and implemented a data-driven CRO program. Within 90 days, conversions tripled and user retention improved by 60%.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[How a complete UX redesign and CRO program tripled conversions and improved retention by 60% for a FinTech startup.]]></excerpt:encoded>
