	<item>
		<title>Our Design Philosophy: Form Meets Function</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>At Opulentia Agency, we don't believe in choosing between beauty and usability. The best designs are both stunning and intuitive.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Our design philosophy is rooted in three principles: clarity, delight, and purpose. Every pixel earns its place. Every interaction should feel intentional. And every design must serve the user's goals.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Opulentia Agency's design philosophy — clarity, delight, and purpose in every pixel.]]></excerpt:encoded>
